text: Ngô Quang Huy (born 28 November 1990) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as an Attacking midfielder for V-League (Vietnam) club Quảng Nam. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:V.League 1 players Category:SHB Da Nang F.C. players
